content.content: 1. The time limits for 2009 under subsections 275 (4), 276 (4), 279 (1), 292 (2) and 330 (1) of the Act are extended to June 30, 2009. O. Reg. 147/09, s. 1.

content.content: 2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Regulation). O. Reg. 147/09, s. 2.
